Remarks. The present specimens agree with previous descriptions, except for minor variations as follows: In the present specimens lateral margins of the telson bears 22-31 spines, while in earlier descriptions only 14-20 spines are reported (
Sars 1885
;
Ii 1964
;
Pillai 1973
). The present specimens measure up to 10.4 mm , which is the maximum size observed.
